{"tid":1614281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼仔話下次和理非要係11月5號全民V煞","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T07:47:20.000Z","uid":14623,"like":72,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"2db97f6669938abd4f0df3bf356da9fd2edb84a2","tid":1614281,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"1號發完夢之後就同之前既英國既鬼仔同學傾呢件事，以下係convo既精髓，原文係最底<br />\n<br />\n經過左連日黎既勇武夢遊，應該要搞返個和理非，而選址應該係一個有意義既地方（其實我個人提議添馬）主題係V煞，每個人都黑衫黑褲v煞mask係添馬睇煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要俾全世界知道香港大部分人都係支持示威者，所以日期一定要11月5號晚，guy fawkes night，咁先至有共鳴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r03qwc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr03qwc7.jpg&h=fbae3e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6s6Z6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6s6Z6e.jpg&h=4e061972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYupMNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYupMNa.jpg&h=47bb48e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣可以參考下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_-gHVGOoE48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_-gHVGOoE48&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7Ex5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=214346c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_-gHVGOoE48</a><br />\n要重演呢個scene<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要和理非，11月5號<span style=\"color: red;\">全民V煞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Beneath this mask there is an idea, and ideas are bulletproof</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oQhLdqTFGpY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoQhLdqTFGpY&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7Ex5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=343e9b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oQhLdqTFGpY</a><br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\ntbh i think the protest today, well at least from what ive seen, is sort of too violent for u lil pussy (佢屌我pussy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) to participate, which is y i think <span style=\"color: red;\">u guys would need another peaceful protest, sth similar to the 2 million people one</span><br />\n<br />\nive seen the vendetta mask in a couple of protests vids now and the fireworks in one of the vids sparked me, u know guy fawkes night and the vendetta movie right? <span style=\"color: red;\">the next huge peaceful protest should be on 5/11, i know its a weekday but imagine everyone with the v mask on the streets marching to a place, watch some fireworks and disappear, and it has to be on guy fawkes night as well, since we do fireworks as well in the uk, what u guys need is a message, that the majority of hong kong is with you guys</span>"},{"pid":"8342efb8bb67118f4ebdaa2bfab6d4c78e9ec41b","tid":1614281,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"a9177be5ae757bd34f0ffc95dc4ff6a3fa04ce6a","tid":1614281,"uid":308014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"463b06751002185ae69168c4f571f139384bb776","tid":1614281,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:44:22.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"2360291bfc0cc9f575f6ebf01f50abb8e140431c","tid":1614281,"uid":147724,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"係應該和理非一次再集氣   同埋真係搞得成又會震驚全世界"},{"pid":"16ba5738632af5cd426011d499f84e192829b07c","tid":1614281,"uid":14623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"仲要係guy fawkes night 英美都有event 呢個故事家傳戶曉 一定勁大迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5591561b441212ca71074158e1b1580875059d8b","tid":1614281,"uid":14623,"